snippet.title: Meghan Markle wins privacy battle with British tabloid | Today Show Australia
snippet.description:
Subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/2n4QLnx | Meghan Markle has won the latest stage of her privacy battle after a UK court dismissed an appeal by Associated Newspapers, the publishers of The Mail on Sunday, over an earlier ruling against them regarding the publishing of extracts of a letter written by the Duchess of Sussex to her father, Thomas Markle, in August 2018.

(Broadcast December 3, 2021) Get more TODAY at: http://9Soci.al/KzNl50GjSJk
